data.description: Just minutes from highway access, conveniently located near Downtown Summerlin and local shopping. Popular floorplan with an additional enclosed den and a loft! Covered patio and garden landscaping. Nestled in one of Summerlin's subdivisions across from Las Vegas Baseball Park and Golden Knights Practice arena, this beautiful home also has two neighboring parks, community pool and clubhouse! Motivated seller, bring an offer!
